EU Provides Guidance on Managing Carbon Capture, Storage Risks

-- B y   M a t h e w   C a r r
-- 
2011-04-01T06:56:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-01/eu-provides-guidance-on-managing-carbon-capture-storage-risks.html
The European Union provided guidance
for member states on the risks faced by carbon-capture and
storage projects over their lifetimes.  The documents are to help ensure safe storage of the
greenhouse gas blamed for  climate change  because countries in
the bloc are introducing laws governing so-called CCS projects
by June 25,  according to documents  on the EU website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mathew Carr in London at 
